      a: "Customer data is retained only for the duration of the engagement plus a short post-termination window. Within 30 days of contract termination, all customer content is deleted from production systems; certified deletion documentation is available on request. Customers may also delete individual records on demand from within the product at any time, with deletion propagating to backups in the next rotation cycle."
